OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome bright or sunny intervals
OL,6,Fand scattered showers this morning.
OL,7,FBecoming cloudy with fewer showers
OL,8,Fduring this afternoon. Fresh
OL,9,Foccasionally strong west or
OL,10,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy with occasional rain,
OL,13,Fthis becoming heavy and persistent in
OL,14,Fthe north and west later. Windy night
OL,15,Fwith fresh to strong southwesterly
OL,16,Fwinds, gales over coasts and hills
OL,17,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
