OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FHeavy rain in the morning
OL,6,Fclearing to sunny spells and a few
OL,7,Fshowers in the afternoon. Windy at
OL,8,Ffirst.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCold on
OL,11,FFriday with rain and snow showers.
OL,12,FShowers or longer spells of rain on
OL,13,FSaturday, snow on hills at first.
OL,14,FFurther rain followed by showers on
OL,15,FSunday.
